The paper deals with visual tracking using convolutional networks, which is a topic related to computer vision (cs.CV). The paper also discusses the use of k-means algorithm and online learning, which are techniques commonly used in machine learning (cs.LG, cs.AI). Additionally, the paper involves the processing of video data, which falls under multimedia (cs.MM). Finally, the paper discusses the use of sparse representations, which is a topic related to neural networks (cs.NE).
